{
  "stem": "2723.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But, incredibly as it may sound, I have more horrific recollection of that period than I had because in its insanity, there was more order.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "While I was in Auschwitz, there was more terror.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But there was more order, and the work itself was dextrously-- sorry, was taxing for my dexterity.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it wasn't arduous like this was, to the point where I felt I can't anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I think I became pretty, pretty frightened that I wouldn't be able to carry on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And carry on I did want to.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know why, but I did, because I was still believing that all this is just-- it's not real.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's just some kind of temporary nightmare.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it must've been for about a month.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At the end of that month, the-- the more [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] fit-looking-- it sounds such a ridiculous statement, but that's exactly what they told us-- were to go elsewhere for work.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I really thought we were going to be put to death, because I didn't think I looked fit anymore.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But strangely enough, when you've been well built and tall and fit, I guess it took somewhat longer for me to really get debilitated, and I still was considered reasonably fit to go to work.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the third place was, again, a very small number this time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't know why I was selected-- I have no idea-- to go to an actual part of German industry.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
